      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. The exterior paint retains its original factory luster with absolutely no scratches, dents, or blemishes. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with leather seats that look brand new and all electronic features functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is flawless, providing a smooth and powerful driving experience that feels exactly as it did when it first left the dealership. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle of this caliber in truly perfect condition.",
