    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty to believe it. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and treated with so much love. It literally looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single mark or blemish anywhere! I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to let it go, but I\u2019m looking for someone who will cherish it as much as I have. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
