    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3, a masterclass in atmospheric induction. The S54 straight-six has undergone a comprehensive preventative maintenance suite, including high-tolerance rod bearing replacement and a full VANOS system rebuild to ensure precise valve timing. The longitudinal chassis integrity is guaranteed via a reinforced rear subframe, eliminating the common structural fatigue associated with this platform. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, providing unparalleled mechanical grip. The suspension geometry remains true with fresh bushings throughout, and the factory finish exhibits no clear-coat failure or panel misalignment. This is a mechanically sorted, turn-key example for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
