    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment by its sole owner. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Every panel is original, and the wheels are free of any curb rash. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the premium leather remains supple with no wear on the bolsters, and the original protective films are still present on some of the high-tech interface displays. Mechanically, the car is flawless, supported by a comprehensive folder of dealership service records showcasing preventative maintenance performed well ahead of schedule. With a spotless undercarriage and an engine bay detailed to perfection, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its model. It is a rare find for a buyer who demands nothing less than perfection.",
